{"tid":2409473,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"標普期貨創新高，油價13個月新高，鉑金六年多最高","createTime":"2021-02-15T23:46:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T23:46:47.000Z","uid":84046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"14b93b5fdbd7cfe59b3840b3dda3f134359ac9bb","tid":2409473,"uid":84046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T23:46:47.000Z","msg":"全球所有市場都升，現金就係廢紙<br />\n<br />\n週一歐股尾盤時，美股三大股指期貨保持漲勢且均漲超0.4%，其中標普500指數期貨創歷史最高。富時中國A50指數期貨維持逾0.1%的漲幅，MSCI除日本外的亞太股票指數也創歷史最高。全球股市迎來11連漲，創2009年以來最長連漲週期。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x25ddKW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx25ddKW.png&h=219f2e70&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yqj5Pih.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyqj5Pih.png&h=dafa3c4c&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}